Psionic_Lash.help: You channel energy into your whip and lash out at your foe, dealing high energy damage and causing fire damage over time. Lash has longer range than most melee attacks. It will reduce the target's damage resistance and also has a chance to knockdown your target.
Psionic_Lash.shortHelp: Ranged (Close), Moderate DMG (Psionic), Minor DoT (Fire), -Rech (Foe), Chance for Knockdown (Foe)
Psionic_Lash.targetHelp: You are on fire and burning. Your attack speed has also been reduced.

Psionic_Thrash.help: You create a whip of pure psionic energy and make an impressive sweep, causing psionic damage to enemies within a wide cone. Affected targets are seared by this attack and suffer additional fire damage over time. They also are unable to fly and suffer both reduced movement and attack speed. There is also a chance that affected targets will be knocked back.
Psionic_Thrash.shortHelp: Ranged (Short Cone), High DMG(Psionic), High DoT (Fire), -Speed (Foe, All), Chance for Knockback
Psionic_Thrash.targetHelp: You are on fire and burning. You are also unable to fly and both your movement and attack speeds are reduced.

Psionic_Pulse.help: You unleash a powerful pulse of psionic energy that strikes all targets around you. This pulse is of variable strength, but always deals a significant amount of psionic damage and reduces the attack speed of affected targets. There is also a high chance that affected targets will be stunned.
Psionic_Pulse.shortHelp: PBAoE, High to Superior DMG (Psionic), -Rech (Foe), Chance for Stun (Foe)
Psionic_Pulse.targetHelp: Your attack speed has been reduced. You may also be stunned.
